{
  "stem": "7358.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A few months later, they rounded up all the-- they decided to-- oh, they issued an order for people immediately to wear the-- the-- the yellow Star of David, to identify the Jews.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they started to evict people from their houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They created a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Our town was sort of divided-- it was divided.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It had two main streets running across.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took one quarter of the city-- of the town-- and they-- I would say maybe 80 homes or something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they shoved in all the people from the entire town into that area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They erected a fence.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they had-- Ukrainian police patrolled the only gate that was available to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Food became very scarce.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They-- they handed out very small portions of bread to each family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people were beginning to-- to look emaciated already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You could see people in the streets looking very slim, and children running around with their knees bulging out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And at that point, the Germans decided to build a road from Ludwipol to another town called Bresna.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- because our area was a poor area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and there-- there were not too many roads available for the German war machine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did that, my sister did that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father did that periodically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he used to help my mother in-- in-- in the photography store.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What the Germans did, they-- since we were professionals, they allowed us to live on-- in our-- they gave us the houses facing the main street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- and the fence that used to go around the entire ghetto did not-- was not erected in front of our houses.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was erected between the houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So our, our front windows were facing freedom, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
